So you're an [[Introvert]] and you want to develop your [[Secondary Function]].  How do you do that?  According to the [[Marketing-Vs.-Engineering Exegesis]], you'd do some market research.  But how do you do ''that?''

----

* ''Te:'' Find out the specifications that you need to meet: learn a form into which you can pour your thoughts and observations.

* ''Se:'' Go see what's happening in some public arena so you can join the party.

* ''Ne:'' Go see what's happening in some public arena so you can one-up it or otherwise add things to it that it lacks.

* ''Fe:'' Go to some public get-together and figure out the signs that people are using to define themselves and their relationships.
